ABB Wins $80 Million Power Order for Itaipu Hydro Plant in Paraguay

-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 
2011-07-12T12:03:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/abb-wins-80-million-power-order-for-itaipu-hydro-plant-in-paraguay.html
ABB Ltd. (ABBN)  won orders worth about $80
million from Itaipu Binacional, the operator of the Itaipu
hydroelectric power plant, to build a new substation in  Paraguay 
and expand an existing installation, ABB said today in an e-
mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Verschuur at 
 pverschuur@bloomberg.net  